reviewText: It came early then It said so that was awesome. Only thing so far that bad about it was the wrapping over the case had rip but that's no big deal!

I loved the first two Rozen Maiden DVDs, and I loved this one as well. I have watched it through three times already. The scene in which the Rozen Maidens, Jun, and Nori act out the tale of Snow White is priceless (Hina ichigo: "There's not really seven of us, but we're the seven dwarves.") The DVD is worth buying for that alone.
